OL,3,CFour-year-old boy hallucinated after
OL,4,Cdrinking slushie, mother says
OL,6,FParents of children under four are
OL,7,Fbeing urged to think twice before
OL,8,Fallowing their children to have
OL,9,Fslushies after a young boy ended up in
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,FFour-year-old Albie Pegg was rushed to
OL,13,Fhospital after he started clawing at
OL,14,Fhis own face, biting himself and
OL,15,Fhallucinating after drinking a slushie
OL,16,Fat a bowling alley.
OL,18,FBy the time the family got to A&E,
OL,19,FAlbie was "a deadweight", his mother,
OL,20,FBeth Green, told Good Morning Britain
OL,21,Fon Tuesday.
