OL,3,CFour-year-old boy hallucinated after
OL,4,Cdrinking slushie, mother says
OL,6,F"I was very scared and I wanted my
OL,7,Fdaddy to pick me up," the four-year-
OL,8,Fold said.
OL,10,FMs Green said she feared that her son
OL,11,Fcould die, adding: "It was absolutely
OL,12,Fawful and it was just so
OL,13,Fheartbreaking."
OL,15,FDoctors said it was the additive
OL,16,Fglycerol in the slushie that had
OL,17,Fcaused Albie's illness, rather than
OL,18,Fthe colouring, which gives the drink
OL,19,Fits slushie texture.
