OL,3,CFour-year-old boy hallucinated after
OL,4,Cdrinking slushie, mother says
OL,6,FThe best-known brand of slushie drink,
OL,7,FSlush Puppie, has said the recipes for
OL,8,Fits drinks do not contain glycerol.
OL,10,FThe drinks shouldn't be consumed by
OL,11,Fchildren aged four or under, Professor
OL,12,FRobin May from the Food Standards
OL,13,FAgency (FSA) said.
