OL,3,CFour-year-old boy hallucinated after
OL,4,Cdrinking slushie, mother says
OL,6,FHe added that the amount of glycerol
OL,7,Fconsumed should be limited in all
OL,8,Fchildren under 10, as a large quantity
OL,9,Fof the additive can have adverse
OL,10,Feffects in small bodies.
OL,12,F"The issue is if you consume a lot of
OL,13,Fglycerol, fast, particularly if you're
OL,14,Frelatively small ... That can lead
OL,15,Fwater to rush into your blood vessels
OL,16,Fessentially to compensate," he said,
OL,17,Fcomparing the experience to
OL,18,Fdehydration.
