OL,3,CFour-year-old boy hallucinated after
OL,4,Cdrinking slushie, mother says
OL,6,FChildren's bodies can't deal with
OL,7,Fglycerol as quickly as they deal with
OL,8,Fnormal sugars in the blood, and as a
OL,9,Fresult it can cause shock, low blood
OL,10,Fsugar and lack of consciousness.
OL,12,FAround 50 million slushie drinks are
OL,13,Fsold in the UK each year, according to
OL,14,Fthe FSA, and there were five cases
OL,15,Fsimilar to Albie's in the last three
OL,16,Fyears.
